dct_title_s: Harbor Lines Delaware River Cooper Point to Cooper Creek, Camden, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map shows Camden between Cooper Creek and the Delaware River. Map shows soundings, curves of depth at 6, 12,18, and 24 feet, pierhead and bulkhead lines, and a sketch showing the location of monuments. Map also shows the Delaware River, parts of Camden, Cooper Creek, and Petty Island.
